name: Salty Fish Go!
description:
SaltyFish Go is a casual runner game.
Play with the most celebrated fish in human history. Slash skirt, slash mice, slash other fishes, collect salts, buy gorgeous outfit, run like a superhero (sorry... superfish), jump onto platforms, avoid cat and discover the infinite space.


Main features:
- You control SaltyFish as he runs, jumps, slides, and more!
- Extremely addictive “just one more time” gameplay!
- Fast-paced and simple core gameplay
- Random generated street levels.
- Lift up girl's skirts, score 100.
- Collect salts to unlock over Fish outfits.
- SaltyFish emoticons and background.

Join SaltyFish on his most epic journey yet!
